    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A variant of photogravure in which the plate is dusted with rosin to create an irregular grain pattern with enhanced ink-holding capabilities.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
